  <CalDefinition Description="To improve the User Experience, a calibration defined as cal_DABMuteOn and cal_DABMuteOff will be used to create a mute/unmute ramp time when a DAB signal is acquired." Name="DAB_DABMuteOff" References="GIS-313-1920 Acquisition time after changing preset memory" Usage="LOW,MID,HIGH,GEM,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,ENTRY_VCU,VCU">
